---
import Button from "@/components/input/Button.astro";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="API"
  description="Fand API 文档入口。"
  keywords={["fand", "api", "javadocs", "minecraft", "plugin"]}
  canonical="/javadocs"
>
  <header class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl flex-col items-center px-4 pt-32 pb-20 text-center lg:pt-36">
    <img src="/assets/logo/256x.png" alt="" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-3xl" />
    <div class="tech-label mt-8">PLUGIN API</div>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white md:text-7xl">Fand API</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-8 text-gray-300">
      Fand 正在补齐统一配置、日志、Tag、注册表、世界生成等 API。在线 Javadoc 发布后，这里会指向版本化文档。
    </p>

    <div class="glass-panel mt-10 w-full rounded-3xl p-6 text-left">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">当前入口</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-gray-300">
        在正式文档站接入前，可以先从 GitHub 查看 `fand-api` 模块源码和示例。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <Button variant="filled" href="https://github.com/MC20018/Fand" external>GitHub</Button>
        <Button variant="outlined" href="/software/fand">核心介绍</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
</Layout>
